<tr id="L136"><td><a href="#L136">136</a></td><td>TUVOK:  That is precisely what I attempted to do.</td></tr>

<tr id="L137"><td><a href="#L137">137</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  There must be some reason why your mind brought us here. Maybe this memory is connected to the girl in some way. How long ago is this?</td></tr>

<tr id="L138"><td><a href="#L138">138</a></td><td>TUVOK:  Stardate 9521, approximately eighty years ago.</td></tr>

<tr id="L139"><td><a href="#L139">139</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  Who were you fighting?</td></tr>

<tr id="L140"><td><a href="#L140">140</a></td><td>TUVOK:  The Klingons.</td></tr>

