<tr id="L142"><td><a href="#L142">142</a></td><td>TUVOK:  This battle was precipitated by an incident that took place three days earlier.</td></tr>

<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Gamma shift crew quarters</td></tr>
<tr id="L143"><td><a href="#L143">143</a></td><td>RAND:  All right, gamma shift, time to defend the Federation against gaseous anomalies.</td></tr>

<tr id="L144"><td><a href="#L144">144</a></td><td>JANEWAY:  Gaseous anomalies. We were charting a gaseous anomaly on Voyager.</td></tr>

<tr id="L145"><td><a href="#L145">145</a></td><td>TUVOK:  And that's when my problem began.</td></tr>

